  "title": "Driver, Prime Mover",
  "description": "<p><strong>Interested applicants should WhatsApp 9820 6631 to apply. No quota. Foreigners do not apply. </strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>$1,500 Joining Bonus! T&amp;Cs apply.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WYN2000 is a 3PL niche provider offering customized logistics solution in transport and warehousing. We pride ourselves on directing meaningful solutions to our customers. We have expanded our business services across different points of the supply chain process which make us the preferred logistics partner in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Main Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Transport containers or loose cargo from one location to another location</li>\n  <li>Trucking of containers into yards</li>\n  <li>Familiar with PSA operations</li>\n  <li>Ensure safety of cargo and vehicle</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Class 4/ 5 driving licence</li>\n  <li>Must have min 2 years' driving experience as a Prime Mover Driver in Singapore</li>\n  <li>Follow Singapore traffic regulations and PSA/ Jurong Port requirements</li>\n  <li>Observe and conform to company's safety regulations</li>\n  <li>Able and willing to start work early based on job needs</li>\n  <li>Accident free and clean driving records</li>\n</ul>",
